title._content: Winter view in Stockholm City, Sweden

description._content: City view in winter from the terrace of the Royal Swedish Academy of Fine Arts. In the middle is the House of Nobility in the Old Town and to the right is the tower of Riddarholmen Church. Stadsvy på vintern från Konstakademiens terrass. I mitten Riddarhuset i Gamla stan och till höger Riddarholmskyrkans torn. Parish (socken): Stockholm Province (landskap): Uppland Municipality (kommun): Stockholm County (län): Stockholm Photograph by: Carl Curman Date: 1900 Format: Print Persistent URL: www.kms.raa.se/cocoon/bild/show-image.html?id=16000300029291 Read more about the photo database (in english): www.kms.raa.se/cocoon/bild/about.html
